VALUES
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00588', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一首4分鐘的音樂，若以取樣頻率為44.1KHz，取樣樣本為2個8bits（立體聲）的數字儲存，則所 需的儲存空間大小約略等於：', '["21.17Mbytes", "169.34Mbytes", "13.2Mbytes", "132Kbytes"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00589', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關網際網路的描述何者正確？', '["相同網路區段內的電腦，不可以直接傳遞IP封包，需要路由器協助", "要判斷兩台網路上電腦是否在相同網路區段，可分別將其IP位址與子網路遮罩做XOR運算，看 結果是否相同", "DNS伺服器主要功能為正向名稱解析（Forward Name Resolution），也就是將輸入網址轉為對應 的IP位址", "網址的格式為“主機名稱.網域名稱”，其中的主機名稱使用長度沒有任何限制"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00590', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '由多個遠端主機在同一時段傳送許多訊息給目標主機，使目標主機在短時間內因接收過多訊息而癱 瘓，這種網路攻擊稱為：', '["分散式阻斷攻擊（DistributedDoS）", "回覆氾濫攻擊（SmurfFloodingAttack）", "死亡偵測攻擊（Ping-of-DeathAttack）", "分割重組攻擊（TeardropAttack）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00591', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '自駕車是傳統汽車運輸能力加上整合感知器、電腦視覺、高速運算及全球定位系統等技術而有的現 代高科技產物。請問根據美國國家公路交通安全管理局（NHTSA）所定義的自駕車等級（Level）， 其中「駕駛人可以在某些有限服務區域內讓車輛自動駕駛，車內所有人僅充當乘客無需參與駕駛工 作」，是屬於下列那一個等級？', '["等級2", "等級3", "等級4", "等級5"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00592', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '所謂智慧物聯網AIoT（ArtificialIntelligenceofThings）是指人工智慧（AI）結合物聯網（IoT）的科 技。這項技術採用了一種特殊的分散式網路計算，將運算資源直接嵌入端點設備，能夠有效降低網 路寬頻的使用量，同時加速及時運算。請問這項特殊的計算方式，稱為：', '["邊緣運算EdgeComputing", "高效能運算HighPerformanceComputing", "雲端運算CloudComputing", "數位計算DigitalComputing"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00593', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '電子商務交易機制的安全是電子商務可以推動很主要的原因。以前當信用卡遺失，陌生人就有可能 拿到信用卡卡號、到期年限及信用卡背面末三碼，也就可以在電子商務上進行消費。為了改善這個 問題，有一個新的安全機制產生。當消費者在網路上進行刷卡消費時，系統會自動跳出驗證視窗， 消費者須輸入認證密碼才能進行刷卡付款，而驗證碼通常是由系統發簡訊送到持卡者的手機上。 請問這樣的安全機制，是下列那一種：', '["3D認證機制（3DSecure）", "網路銀行憑證", "金融XML憑證（FinancialeXtensibleMarkupLanguage）", "代理人伺服器（ProxyServer）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00594', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '電腦中的2進位系統對整數的表示法，有帶符號大小（Signed-magnitude），1’s補數（1’sComplement）， 2’s補數（2’sComplement）。假設使用8位元來儲存整數，請問下列何者正確？', '["96的帶符號大小表示法為11000000", "-96的1’s補數表示法為10011111", "96的2’s補數表示法為01110000", "-96的2’s補數表示法為10011111"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00595', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '電腦常見的一些數碼系統可以用來表示10進位數字，請問下列何者正確？', '["9的BCD碼為1001", "3的2421碼為0100", "8的84-2-1碼為1001", "4的超三碼為0100"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00596', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '電腦的數字系統用來儲存浮點數可以根據 IEEE 754 的規範，IEEE 754 定義了 Single、Double、 Extended及Quadruple等四種浮點數格式。若要表示10進位的 -22.5，根據IEEE754的single格式， 請問b b b …b （第31~23位元）的值為何？', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0c700c30-moex-00597', 'elementary-0c700c30', 'elementary-0c700c30-moex-112-e8c1e471', 'sub-elementary-0c700c30-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '30 29 23', '["010000011", "110010011", "011000011", "110000011"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1e9384d08aea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "eb10e6559f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "508", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "資料處理大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "統計"}'::jsonb, NULL)
